    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>After </strong>5 min, remove the lid and stir continuously until the linguine has cooked (approx. 5 min), adding more water if needed</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong>&nbsp;stirring the sauce releases the starch from the pasta, making it creamier</p>",
